query:
UPDATE activity_spots aspo
JOIN places p ON aspo.name = p.name AND aspo.spotType = CASE 
  WHEN p.type = 'dive_site' THEN 'dive_site'
  WHEN p.type = 'surf_spot' THEN 'surf_spot'
  WHEN p.type = 'snorkeling_spot' THEN 'snorkeling_spot'
END
SET aspo.placeId = p.id
WHERE aspo.placeId IS NULL
